#Grammer for parser 
Aim 
    Unambigous 
    No left recursion (even though parser allows it)
    No left factoring 

Writting grammer for SIL language http://athena.nitc.ac.in/~kmurali/Compiler/sil.html

Function and array is not required for week 2 

#Grammer

 delcalaration section
 

start           ->  (global)(main)
global          ->  "decl" (decl-state) "enddecl"                                                                                           #global declaration part
decl-state      ->  (declint)(decl-state) | (declbool)(decl-state) | (declintarray)(decl-state) | (declboolarray)(decl-state) | "NULL"        #global declation types
declint         ->  "integer"


main            ->                                          #main function definition


